<h2 id="building-the-form">Building the Form <a class="headerlink" href="form-post#building-the-form" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>In build form, let's see here, let's build the form! Just like normal
use <code>$builder-&gt;add()</code> - the first field is <code>nickname</code> and set it to a <code>text</code>
type. The second field is <code>avatarNumber</code>. In this case, the value will be
a number from 1 to 6. So we <em>could</em> use the <code>number</code> type. But instead, use
<code>choice</code>. For the <code>choices</code> option, I'll paste in an array that goes from
1 to 6:</p>
